Well as long as your not gonna spoon feed him then its all good. I wanna see someone make a good server for once and it isnt gonna happen unless he either does it alone or with a team with all the same goals :). Anyway i can probly provide some links to websites & tuts if he needs it. To be a help to his success.

when i made my first server i was overwhelm with everyone asking to become staff on the server, and i didnt wanna ban them or id have no players, so your first server is the hardest to care for. But youll learn soon enough of the pains of owning one. lol
